          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>PHORIA AND<a href=\"http://www.phoriajewellery.com\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">WWW.PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</span></a> ARE TRADING NAMES OF PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD (“THE COMPANY”, “WE”, “OUR”, “US”).</p><p>THESE TERMS & CONDITIONS APPLY TO ALL INTERACTIONS, PURCHASES, AND USE OF THIS WEBSITE.</p><p>BY USING THIS WEBSITE AND/OR PLACING AN ORDER, YOU AGREE TO THESE TERMS & CONDITIONS.</p><p>IF YOU HAVE QUESTIONS, CONTACT US AT: INFO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</p>"
          }
